articles.title: Healthier diets may lead to greater physical fitness - News-Medical.Net
articles.description: A healthy diet is associated with greater physical fitness in middle-aged adults, according to research published today in the European Journal of Preventive Cardiology, a journal of the European Society of Cardiology.
